      • fetchWaitTime

        public final long fetchWaitTime
        Time tasks spent waiting for remote shuffle blocks. This only includes the time blocking on shuffle input data. For instance if block B is being fetched while the task is still not finished processing block A, it is not considered to be blocking on block B.
